#. Welcome message
msgid "welcome_message"
msgstr ""
"✨ <b>Welcome!</b> ✨\n\n"
"📩 <b>Send messages or any type of media</b> (📷 photos, 🎥 videos, 🎞️ GIFs, 📄 documents, 🎵 audios, etc.), and the bot will forward them "
"to you without revealing your identity.\n\n"
"🔄 The original forwarding name will be <b>removed</b> and replaced by the bot's name, ensuring complete anonymity.\n\n"
"🔒 <b>Your privacy is our priority!</b>\n\n"
"⚠️ <i>Note:</i>\n"
" ❌ Buttons and captions will be <b>automatically removed</b>.\n"
" 📝 <b>Captions:</b> Only photos, videos, and GIFs can have captions.\n\n"
"👉 <b>Try it now! Send your media and see how it works</b>"

